GREENE
v.
WHITE 424P16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 1, 2016 Corey Delon Greene, for Greene, Corey Delon. Kristin Jo Uicker, Assistant Attorney General, Sarah Kirkman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of November 2016 by Petitioner for Notice of Appeal:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 2nd of December 2016."
